output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Number: - Present: CMF:11200014 - This confirms it's electoral propaganda
2. Refers to candidate: - Directly mentions and tags George Simion - Clear presidential candidate reference - Also mentions other parties (PSD, PNL, USR) in negative context
3. Addresses wide population: - Paid advertisement with 20,000-24,999 impressions - Uses inclusive language ("ne-au adus") - Calls for action ("Duminică votez") - Targets 500,001-1,000,000 potential viewers
4. Electoral objective: - Clear call to vote for George Simion - Contains campaign hashtags (#GeorgeSimion #Președinte) - Explicitly states "Duminică votez altceva" - Criticizes other parties to promote AUR's candidate
5. Journalism: - Not journalistic content - Clear campaign material with political messaging
6. Personal opinion: - While expressing opinions about other parties, this is clearly structured as campaign material - Contains official campaign elements (CMF number, hashtags)

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains official campaign elements (CMF number) - Direct call to vote for a specific candidate - Paid distribution targeting large audience - Clear electoral messaging and campaign hashtags - Negative messaging about other parties - Timing during electoral period
conclusion.message-for-police: Voga Design & Architecture, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin difuzarea unui material de propaganda electorala (ID postare Facebook: 1922465028238746) dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Materialul prezinta caracteristici clare de propaganda electorala: numar unic de inregistrare CMF:11200014, indeamna explicit la vot pentru candidatul George Simion, contine hashtag-uri de campanie (#GeorgeSimion #Președinte), si este distribuit ca reclama platita pe Facebook cu impact intre 20.000-24.999 impresii. Mesajul denigreaza alte partide si candidati, promovand in mod direct un candidat la presedintie, incalcand astfel prevederile legale privind perioada de campanie electorala.
